---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Project Management Case Studies - SP Consulting">
  <Navigation />

  <main class="pt-20">
    {/* Hero Section */}
    <section class="bg-primary text-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Project Management Case Studies</h1>
        <p class="text-xl">Real-world success stories in project management and process improvement.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Main Content Section */}
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50"> {/* Added light background */}
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl"> {/* Increased max-width */}
        <div class="space-y-12">

          {/* Case Study 1: e-Commerce Fulfillment */}
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md"> {/* Reduced shadow */}
             {/* UPDATED Title */}
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">eCommerce Fulfillment Center Launch Optimization</h2>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6"> {/* Added margin-bottom */}
              <span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">
                eCommerce
              </span>
              <span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">
                PMO Setup
              </span>
              <span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">
                Value Stream Mapping
              </span>
               <span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">
                Process Improvement
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-6">
              <img
                src="/assets/fulfillment-center.png" {/* Placeholder - UPDATE PATH */}
                alt="eCommerce Fulfillment Center Optimization"
                class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-md mb-4" {/* Reduced shadow */}
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            {/* Removed introductory P tag */}
            <div class="space-y-6"> {/* Increased spacing */}
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-800">Business Challenge</h3> {/* Styled heading */}
                {/* UPDATED Content */}
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                 The company's rapid growth required accelerated launch of fulfillment buildings. However, constant delays in identifying building type and location by demand planning led to premium costs for real estate agreements and construction. This compression also forced engineering and launch teams into unrealistic working hours.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-800">Approach</h3> {/* Styled heading */}
                 {/* UPDATED Content - Using list */}
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 pl-2">
                    <li>Conducted Value Stream Mapping to accurately determine end-to-end lead times across the entire operational workflow.</li>
                    <li>Developed and presented a business case for establishing a Project Management Office (PMO) with a robust stage-gate process, ensuring complete visibility and control over project lifecycles.</li>
                    <li>Performed detailed evaluation of lead times associated with each process deliverable, enabling targeted improvements and resource allocation.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-800">Results</h3> {/* Styled heading */}
                 {/* UPDATED Content - Using list */}
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 pl-2">
                  <li>Implemented a centralized Salesforce data repository for the complete network of fulfillment centers, providing real-time dashboard visualizations for executive oversight.</li>
                  <li>Established transparent timelines for functional deliverables and enhanced visibility of the entire development process for all cross-functional team members.</li>
                  <li>Achieved 20% cost avoidance due to timely, data-driven decisions.</li>
                  <li>Significantly reduced the risk of delays in launching new Fulfillment centers.</li>
                  <li>Optimized the demand planning process by incorporating lead times based on building type.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Case Study 2: Hybrid Methodology */}
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md"> {/* Reduced shadow */}
            {/* UPDATED Title */}
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Accelerating Product Development via Hybrid Methodology</h2>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6"> {/* Added margin-bottom */}
              <span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">
                Agile Transformation
              </span>
               <span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">
                Hybrid Methodology
              </span>
              <span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">
                Manufacturing
              </span>
              <span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">
                Process Improvement
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-6">
              <img
                src="/assets/waterfall-implementation.png" {/* Placeholder - UPDATE PATH */}
                alt="Hybrid Agile/Waterfall Implementation for Manufacturing"
                class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-md mb-4" {/* Reduced shadow */}
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
             {/* Removed introductory P tag */}
            <div class="space-y-6"> {/* Increased spacing */}
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-800">Business Challenge</h3> {/* Styled heading */}
                {/* UPDATED Content */}
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                 Recurring product release delays undermined customer commitments due to: <strong class="font-medium">Shifting Requirements</strong> (Continuous specification changes driven by ongoing customer feedback integration) and <strong class="font-medium">Process Rigidity</strong> (A linear Waterfall development approach where early-stage modifications caused extensive timeline disruptions).
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-800">Approach â€“ Process Improvement</h3> {/* Styled heading */}
                {/* UPDATED Content - Using list */}
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 pl-2">
                  <li>Conducted comprehensive Agile methodology training across the team.</li>
                  <li>Established short-cycle increment planning to prioritize immediate objectives and enable faster feedback.</li>
                  <li>Incorporated a dedicated Product Owner role alongside the NPD Project Manager for clearer focus.</li>
                  <li>Leveraged the Agile framework to enhance the frequency and quality of cross-functional communication.</li>
                  <li>Emphasized a focus on delivering a well-defined Minimum Viable Product (MVP).</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-800">Results</h3> {/* Styled heading */}
                 {/* UPDATED Content - Using list */}
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 pl-2">
                  <li>Achieved 90% on-time delivery for committed product launch dates, significantly improving reliability.</li>
                  <li>Reduced the overall product development cycle time by 20%.</li>
                  <li>Established a process for continuous customer feedback integration, leading to MVP releases that better addressed core user needs and commanded premium pricing.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* CTA Section */}
          <div class="text-center pt-8"> {/* Added padding-top */}
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors text-lg" /* Larger text */
            >
              Discuss Your Project Challenges
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>